      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, drain the <strong>sliced onion </strong>in a sieve and run under <strong>cold water </strong>until cooled</p><p>Return the <strong>drained onion</strong> to the bowl and add your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong> with<strong> </strong>a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Mix it all together and set aside for later – this is your<strong> quick-pickled pink onion</strong></p>",
